OL,3,CFugitive fraudster arrested in Spain
OL,4,Cafter stealing #300k from pensioner
OL,6,FA fugitive fraudster who fled the UK
OL,7,Fto evade justice after stealing nearly
OL,8,F#300,000 from a vulnerable pensioner
OL,9,Fhas been arrested in Spain.
OL,11,FPamela Gwinnett isolated 89-year-old
OL,12,FJoan Green from her family while
OL,13,Fpretending to act as her carer during
OL,14,Fthe Covid-19 pandemic, transferring
OL,15,Fpower of attorney to herself and
OL,16,Fraiding the pensioner's life savings.
OL,18,FShe used the cash to fund an
OL,19,Fextravagant lifestyle, buying a car
OL,20,Fworth #22,500 and expensive beauty and
OL,21,FBotox treatments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
