PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784234869
OL,3,CFugitive fraudster arrested in Spain
OL,4,Cafter stealing #300k from pensioner
OL,6,FGwinnett fled to Tenerife in 2025 in a
OL,7,Fbid to escape prosecution. She was
OL,8,Fconvicted and sentenced in her absence
OL,9,Fin October 2025 for a string of
OL,10,Foffences, including fraud by abuse of
OL,11,Fposition and theft.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,14,Fit was working with the National Crime
OL,15,FAgency and Spanish authorities to
OL,16,Fbring Gwinnett back to the UK to serve
OL,17,Fher sentence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
