FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784234869
OL,3,CFugitive fraudster arrested in Spain
OL,4,Cafter stealing #300k from pensioner
OL,6,FThe court previously heard how
OL,7,FGwinnett systematically targeted the
OL,8,Felderly resident, from Chorley,
OL,9,FLancashire, while employed as a
OL,10,Fcaregiver at her home.
OL,12,FGwinnett used her position of trust to
OL,13,Fisolate Joan from her loved ones,
OL,14,Fcontrolling her life and blocking her
OL,15,Ffrom seeing her grandchildren and
OL,16,Fgreat-grandchildren, all while
OL,17,Fstripping her of her life savings.
OL,19,FJoan passed away in 2022, before she
OL,20,Fcould see Gwinnett brought to justice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784234869
OL,3,CFugitive fraudster arrested in Spain
OL,4,Cafter stealing #300k from pensioner
OL,6,FInvestigating officers have welcomed
OL,7,Fthe arrest, stating they hope the
OL,8,Fdevelopment will bring a sense of
OL,9,Fclosure to Joan's grieving family.
OL,11,FAs part of her scam Gwinnett made a
OL,12,Fseries of false claims against Mrs
OL,13,FGreen's stepdaughter and step-
OL,14,Fgrandchild including theft and neglect
OL,15,Fbefore she gained power of attorney.
OL,17,FJudge Maher added: "I sincerely hope
OL,18,Fthat Ms Gwinnett is extradited back to
OL,19,Fthe UK to serve this sentence for
OL,20,Fthese egregious offences.
OL,26,@yD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
