PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784234869
OL,3,CFugitive fraudster arrested in Spain
OL,4,Cafter stealing #300k from pensioner
OL,6,F"It is an affront to justice and the
OL,7,Frule of law for this defendant to be
OL,8,Fallowed to remain in Tenerife."
OL,10,FPC Georgia Loughton, the officer in
OL,11,Fcharge of the investigation, said:
OL,12,F"Pamela knowingly defrauded a
OL,13,Fvulnerable woman out of almost
OL,14,F#300,000, cutting off all contact with
OL,15,Fher family and controlling every
OL,16,Faspect of her life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
