FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784234869
OL,3,CFugitive fraudster arrested in Spain
OL,4,Cafter stealing #300k from pensioner
OL,6,F"She was trusted by Joan, and she used
OL,7,Fthis position of trust to her own
OL,8,Ffinancial gain. Joan was isolated from
OL,9,Fher family and denied from seeing her
OL,10,Fgrandchildren and their children.
OL,12,F"Sadly, Joan passed away in 2022,
OL,13,Fhowever we hope that the return of
OL,14,FPamela to the UK to serve her sentence
OL,15,Fgives Joan's family a sense of justice
OL,16,Fas they look to move on with their
OL,17,Flives."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
