CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784234869
OL,3,CFugitive fraudster arrested in Spain
OL,4,Cafter stealing #300k from pensioner
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Helen Critchley,
OL,7,FDistrict Commander for GMP's Bolton
OL,8,Fdistrict, said: "Our teams have worked
OL,9,Falongside the National Crime Agency
OL,10,Fand Spanish authorities to ensure that
OL,11,FGwinnett is brought back to the UK to
OL,12,Fface the consequences of her crimes.
OL,14,F"This arrest highlights our commitment
OL,15,Fto relentlessly pursue those who
OL,16,Fcommit crimes and exploit vulnerable
OL,17,Fpeople in our communities. We will
OL,18,Ftake any necessary action to ensure
OL,19,Fthey face justice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
